                            <comment id="16830937" author="prongs" created="Wed, 1 May 2019 10:24:34 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Attaching patch. Simple Fix, the quantiles need to be cleaned up on S3AInstrumentation.close.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I still think we should also merge&#160;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HADOOP-16248&quot; title=&quot;MutableQuantiles leak memory under heavy load&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;HADOOP-16248&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;HADOOP-16248&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;, as I feel scheduleWithFixedDelay is a much better option than scheduleAtFixedRate, at least it&#160;won&apos;t build up the task queue.&#160;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
